        * Logout from room page. (Redirect to login page and reset token field in db as "------")
    - Routing
        * Login user redirects to room page with any non registered URLs.
        * No login user redirects to login page with any non registered URLS.
2. Room
    - Create
        * Create room notifies to room page seeing users.
        * Create room API working with the correct bonus, fee and size. (Check with DB).
        * Creator redirects to cardplay page.
    - Browse
        * Login user can browse all rooms with the pagination.
            & Pagination not visible for 0 or 1 page list
            & Pagination next and prev correctly get the other list of the rooms
            & Pagination prev button disabled at 1st page.
            & Pagination next button disabled at the last page.
        * Search functionality working fine with the correct pagination.
        * Room status update correctly reflects to room browse. (New Room, Status change, Room Close, Member change)
        * Entry Availability. (Entry only available for members who have enough bounty and room is open)
3. CardPlay
