        * Current player has to place at the bottom, and order should be correct.
        * Starts button
            & Only visible to host.
            & Disable when the members are less than room size.
            & If click, starts the game with randomized cards.
    - While Playing (Test with or no F5)
        * Correctly randomized cards. (HavingCards, DropingCards, RestingCards, Host Turn)
        * 10 seconds timer, and automatic pass after that.
        * Hide Pass button
            & When it's not current player's turn.
            & When currnet player is son.
        * Hide Shut button
            & When it's not current player's turn.
            & When there is no choosed card.
            & When the choosed card is not valid.
            & When the choosed card is against for the previous card while current player is not son.
        * Hide Exit button
            & When it's not current player's turn.
        * Shut the card.
            & Change the turn.
            & Show the player's choosed card.
            & Remove player's havingCards.
            & Last choosedcard should be active with the red border.
            & Reinitialize the timer for the next player.
        * Pass the card.
            & Change the turn.
            & Show the pass banner for 1 sec.
            & Reinitialize the timer for the next player.
        * Exit Request
            & Click Exit button changes the button title with "Cancel" and show "Exit Request" string.
            & Click Cancel button changes the button title with "Exit" and remove "Exit Request" string.
            & F5 should persist all the current status.
        * Son.
            & Son should be passed when the timer is ended.
            & If no one shuts the card from me
                ^ All players get one resting card if there are any available resting cards. (Recalculation - HavingCards, RestingCards)
                ^ Become the son and available to shut any valid cards.
        * Playing End
            & Anyone shuts all the cards, he becomes the winner and status changes from playing to calculation
    - While Calculation (Test with F5 or no)
        * Show all players' having cards.
        * Show Result Modal
            & Modal shows winner or not.
